## Data Sources and Attributions

This project incorporates data from the following sources:

### Kalaallisut-English Dictionary
- Source: Oqaasileriffik (Greenland Language Secretariat)
- Used for glossing and translation (16,819 entries)

### Morphological Analyzer
- Source: GiellaLT/lang-kal (https://github.com/giellalt/lang-kal)
- Greenlandic Finite State Transducer for morphological analysis
- License: GPL v3 or LGPL (check lang-kal repository for details)

### Sentence Alignment Tool
- Tool: hunalign by Daniel Varga (https://github.com/danielvarga/hunalign)
- Used for Danish-Kalaallisut sentence alignment

### Parallel Corpus
- Source: Danish-Kalaallisut government documents
- 6,813 aligned sentence pairs extracted and processed
- Public domain government materials

Users of this project should ensure compliance with the licenses of these
underlying resources, particularly when using the morphological analyzer
(lang-kal) which is distributed under GPL/LGPL.
